---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main id="main">
			<section class="hero" aria-labelledby="hero-title">
				<header class="hero-title">
				<img
					class="hero-avatar"
					src="/me.png"
					alt="Portrait of me innit"
					width="240"
					height="240"
				/>
				<div>
					<h1 class="hero-name">Steven Brennan</h1>
					<h2 class="hero-role">Junior Gameplay Programmer</h2>
				</div>
			</div>
			<p>My name is <strong><a href="https://github.com/inakicalvo" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Iñaki Calvo</a></strong> and I'm a techie with a Bachelor's Degree in Philosophy; that's why I named this Astro theme "Ataraxia" after the philosophical concept — learn more on <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ataraxia" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Wikipedia</a>.</p>
			<p>
				<strong>Ataraxia</strong> is an accessible, lightweight <a href="https://astro.build/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Astro</a> theme designed to showcase your writing. Built on the Official Astro Blog Starter, it includes:
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li>✅ <strong>Astro v6</strong> - Built with the latest Astro features</li>
				<li>✅ <strong>Dark Mode</strong> - Toggle between light and dark themes</li>
				<li>✅ <strong>Tag System</strong> - Organize posts by tags with dedicated tag pages</li>
				<li>✅ <strong>Responsive Design</strong> - Mobile-first with hamburger navigation</li>
				<li>✅ <strong>Content Collections</strong> - Type-safe blog posts with Zod validation</li>
				<li>✅ <strong>SEO Optimized</strong> - Canonical URLs, OpenGraph data, and sitemap</li>
				<li>✅ <strong>RSS Feed</strong> - Auto-generated RSS feed for subscribers</li>
				<li>✅ <strong>MDX Support</strong> - Enhanced markdown with component support</li>
				<li>✅ <strong>Breadcrumb Navigation</strong> - Clear navigation paths</li>
				<li>✅ <strong>Performance</strong> - Optimized images with Sharp</li>
				<li>✅ <strong>Minimal Styling</strong> - Clean design based on Astro Starter Kit: Blog</li>
				<li>✅ <strong>Atkinson Hyperlegible Fonts</strong> - Local variable fonts optimized for readability</li>
				<li>✅ <strong>Accessible</strong> - WCAG 2.2 AA compliant with keyboard navigation and screen reader support</li>
			</ul>

			<p>I started building this theme for my personal blog but it's now open source. Customize it, make it yours, and start sharing your ideas with the world. Happy blogging! ✨</p>
			</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
  .hero-title {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .hero-avatar {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .hero-name {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .hero-role {
    margin: 0.25rem 0 0 0;
    opacity: 0.85;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
</style>